extendedInfo.description: Test your powers of observation and see if you can find the differences in the two photos to become a master detective!This is an unofficial MATTEL Monster High doll series fan application.Do you have keen eyes? Then it won't be difficult for you to find differences between the two pictures in these spot the difference games. These games are all about being sharp and quick. A closed eye, a different haircut. This may seem simple to spot but looks can be deceiving.Find out for yourself and enjoy!Please note, that Monster Highâ¢ and all related trademarks belong to MATTEL.
